columns.name: segments_date
columns.description: Date to which metrics apply. yyyy-MM-dd format, for example, 2018-04-17.

columns.name: segments_device
columns.description: Device to which metrics apply.

columns.name: segments_month
columns.description: Month as represented by the date of the first day of a month. Formatted as yyyy-MM-dd.

columns.name: segments_quarter
columns.description: Quarter as represented by the date of the first day of a quarter. Uses the calendar year for quarters, for example, the second quarter of 2018 starts on 2018-04-01. Formatted as yyyy-MM-dd.

columns.name: segments_week
columns.description: Week as defined as Monday through Sunday, and represented by the date of Monday. Formatted as yyyy-MM-dd.

columns.name: segments_year
columns.description: Year, formatted as yyyy.

columns.name: landing_page_view_resource_name
columns.description: Output only. The resource name of the landing page view. Landing page view resource names have the form: customers/{customer_id}/landingPageViews/{unexpanded_final_url_fingerprint}

columns.name: landing_page_view_unexpanded_final_url
columns.description: Output only. The advertiser-specified final URL.

columns.name: metrics_active_view_cpm
columns.description: Average cost of viewable impressions (active_view_impressions).

columns.name: metrics_active_view_ctr
columns.description: Active view measurable clicks divided by active view viewable impressions. This metric is reported only for display network.

columns.name: metrics_active_view_impressions
columns.description: A measurement of how often your ad has become viewable on a Display Network site.

columns.name: metrics_active_view_measurability
columns.description: The ratio of impressions that could be measured by Active View over the number of served impressions.

columns.name: metrics_active_view_measurable_cost_micros
columns.description: The cost of the impressions you received that were measurable by Active View.

columns.name: metrics_active_view_measurable_impressions
columns.description: The number of times your ads are appearing on placements in positions where they can be seen.

columns.name: metrics_active_view_viewability
columns.description: The percentage of time when your ad appeared on an Active View enabled site (measurable impressions) and was viewable (viewable impressions).

columns.name: metrics_all_conversions
columns.description: The total number of conversions. This includes all conversions regardless of the value of include_in_conversions_metric.

columns.name: metrics_all_conversions_from_interactions_rate
columns.description: All conversions from interactions (as oppose to view through conversions) divided by the number of ad interactions.

columns.name: metrics_all_conversions_from_interactions_value_per_interaction
columns.description: The value of all conversions from interactions divided by the total number of interactions.

columns.name: metrics_all_conversions_value
columns.description: The value of all conversions.

columns.name: metrics_all_conversions_value_per_cost
columns.description: The value of all conversions divided by the total cost of ad interactions (such as clicks for text ads or views for video ads).

columns.name: metrics_average_cost
columns.description: The average amount you pay per interaction. This amount is the total cost of your ads divided by the total number of interactions.

columns.name: metrics_average_cpc
columns.description: The total cost of all clicks divided by the total number of clicks received.

columns.name: metrics_average_cpe
columns.description: The average amount that you've been charged for an ad engagement. This amount is the total cost of all ad engagements divided by the total number of ad engagements.

columns.name: metrics_average_cpm
columns.description: Average cost-per-thousand impressions (CPM).

columns.name: metrics_average_cpv
columns.description: The average amount you pay each time someone views your ad. The average CPV is defined by the total cost of all ad views divided by the number of views.

columns.name: metrics_clicks
columns.description: The number of clicks.

columns.name: metrics_conversions
columns.description: The number of conversions. This only includes conversion actions which include_in_conversions_metric attribute is set to true. If you use conversion-based bidding, your bid strategies will optimize for these conversions.

columns.name: metrics_conversions_from_interactions_rate
columns.description: Conversions from interactions divided by the number of ad interactions (such as clicks for text ads or views for video ads). This only includes conversion actions which include_in_conversions_metric attribute is set to true. If you use conversion-based bidding, your bid strategies will optimize for these conversions.

columns.name: metrics_conversions_from_interactions_value_per_interaction
columns.description: The value of conversions from interactions divided by the number of ad interactions. This only includes conversion actions which include_in_conversions_metric attribute is set to true. If you use conversion-based bidding, your bid strategies will optimize for these conversions.

columns.name: metrics_conversions_value
columns.description: The value of conversions. This only includes conversion actions which include_in_conversions_metric attribute is set to true. If you use conversion-based bidding, your bid strategies will optimize for these conversions.

columns.name: metrics_conversions_value_per_cost
columns.description: The value of conversions divided by the cost of ad interactions. This only includes conversion actions which include_in_conversions_metric attribute is set to true. If you use conversion-based bidding, your bid strategies will optimize for these conversions.

columns.name: metrics_cost_micros
columns.description: The sum of your cost-per-click (CPC) and cost-per-thousand impressions (CPM) costs during this period.

columns.name: metrics_cost_per_all_conversions
columns.description: The cost of ad interactions divided by all conversions.

columns.name: metrics_cost_per_conversion
columns.description: The cost of ad interactions divided by conversions. This only includes conversion actions which include_in_conversions_metric attribute is set to true. If you use conversion-based bidding, your bid strategies will optimize for these conversions.

columns.name: metrics_cross_device_conversions
columns.description: Conversions from when a customer clicks on a Google Ads ad on one device, then converts on a different device or browser. Cross-device conversions are already included in all_conversions.

columns.name: metrics_ctr
columns.description: The number of clicks your ad receives (Clicks) divided by the number of times your ad is shown (Impressions).

columns.name: metrics_engagement_rate
columns.description: How often people engage with your ad after it's shown to them. This is the number of ad expansions divided by the number of times your ad is shown.

columns.name: metrics_engagements
columns.description: The number of engagements. An engagement occurs when a viewer expands your Lightbox ad. Also, in the future, other ad types may support engagement metrics.

columns.name: metrics_impressions
columns.description: Count of how often your ad has appeared on a search results page or website on the Google Network.

columns.name: metrics_interaction_event_types
columns.description: The types of payable and free interactions.

columns.name: metrics_interaction_rate
columns.description: How often people interact with your ad after it is shown to them. This is the number of interactions divided by the number of times your ad is shown.

columns.name: metrics_interactions
columns.description: The number of interactions. An interaction is the main user action associated with an ad format-clicks for text and shopping ads, views for video ads, and so on.

columns.name: metrics_mobile_friendly_clicks_percentage
columns.description: The percentage of mobile clicks that go to a mobile-friendly page.

columns.name: metrics_speed_score
columns.description: A measure of how quickly your page loads after clicks on your mobile ads. The score is a range from 1 to 10, 10 being the fastest.

columns.name: metrics_valid_accelerated_mobile_pages_clicks_percentage
columns.description: The percentage of ad clicks to Accelerated Mobile Pages (AMP) landing pages that reach a valid AMP page.

columns.name: metrics_value_per_all_conversions
columns.description: The value of all conversions divided by the number of all conversions.

columns.name: metrics_value_per_conversion
columns.description: The value of conversions divided by the number of conversions. This only includes conversion actions which include_in_conversions_metric attribute is set to true. If you use conversion-based bidding, your bid strategies will optimize for these conversions.

columns.name: metrics_video_view_rate
columns.description: The number of views your TrueView video ad receives divided by its number of impressions, including thumbnail impressions for TrueView in-display ads.

columns.name: metrics_video_views
columns.description: The number of times your video ads were viewed.
